title: 有冇人而家係澳洲working holiday

replies.msg: 你地而家返緊咩工呀

I vacationer in Australia last year which fell below my expectation. The food is mediocre there. The people are rude and racist. If you ask me whether Australia is a good place to go for your holidays, I wouldnt bet on it. There's nothing worth doing there.
